# Motion & Haptics
- Durations: 120ms (small), 180ms (medium), 240ms (large).
- Easing: standard ease-in-out; spring only for micro-interactions.
- Navigation transitions: subtle push/fade; no parallax.
- Haptics:
  - Light selection on toggles/tab switches.
  - Success on pledge confirmed/badge earned.
  - Warning on destructive actions.

